    "description": {
      "value": "<blockquote><p>Prerequisite: Level 5+ Warlock</p></blockquote><p>As a Bonus Action, you can surround yourself with a magical aura of unsettling energies (visuals can be inspired by your patron). The aura extends 5 feet from you in every direction, but not through &amp;Reference[total cover]. It lasts until you have the &amp;Reference[incapacitated apply=false] condition or you dismiss it as a Bonus Action.</p><p>The aura grants you Advantage on Intimidation checks but Disadvantage on all other Charisma checks. Any other creature that starts its turn in the aura takes your choice of Necrotic, Poison, or Radiant damage equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of 0 damage).</p><p>Once you use this invocation, you cannot use it again until you finish a Short or Long Rest.</p>",
